S.FORM: Chet Aubuchon nilacul u siwkay niza Chet Aubuchon, nalecuhan ciniza i 5 a bulad 18 a demiad 1916 a mihcaan. Chet Aubuchon, u kawaw niza sa, u miunduay. mapatay ciniza i 2005 a mihcaan. namimali ciniza i NBA nu Amilika. sengelacan ku banges niza. nu ayaway a tademaw. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan u piazihan tu sulit nu ayzaay a tabakiay a mikeliday asaca angangan nu kanatal atu sefu Lists of National Basketball Association players
